sequenceDiagram
  box rgb(240, 240, 255) Frontend
    participant U as User
    participant W as Web
  end
  box rgb(255, 240, 240) Backend
    participant A as API
    participant D as DB
  end

  U->>W: Login
  Note right of W: validate input
  W->>A: POST /login
  A->>D: query user
  Note over A,D: audit + rate limit
  D-->>A: user row
  A-->>W: 200 OK
  W-->>U: redirect
